name: Gift Boxes!
description:
THIS LISTING IS FOR ORDERS THAT ARE BEING SHIPPED ONLY

If you would like a gift box, please add one to your shopping cart. Gift boxes greatly increase my cost to ship you your items, because of height restrictions with Canada Post, so I will not add them to your order unless purchased separately. 

Gift boxes options are as follows:

2” x 3” Earring Gift Box
3” x 3” Necklace Gift Box
3” x 3” Bracelet Gift Box
4” x 6” Jewelry Set Gift Box   (holds up 3 pieces, so if you are purchasing 2 or 3 pieces as a gift for the same person, you will only need to purchase 1 of these boxes.)

TURTLEFORD RESIDENTS that choose to use the LOCALPICKUP discount code to remove shipping costs from their order (because they plan on picking up their order) will be given gift boxes for all items ordered at no extra charge, so there is no need to purchase any boxes from this listing.
